“So Fred, you like that headstone? Most expensive one.
But y’know, If I could go back in time and not do what I did, I would. Not saying it’s your fault.
Just, I fucked up. I fucked up, Fred.” Oliver kicks the tombstone as hard as he can but only he gets injured.
He takes out his phone and dials 911. “Hi, yea, I’d like to turn myself in.”